<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>友情链接添加通知</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #0066ff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #666666;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .link-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #0066ff;
color: #ffffff !important;            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>友情链接添加成功</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>尊敬的用户 <%= user_name %>:</p>
            <p>您的友情链接申请已经通过！感谢您对我们的支持。</p>
            <p>您现在可以访问我们的官方网站查看链接：</p>
            <a href="<%= site_href %>" class="link-button"><%= site_name %></a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
